descriptionHtml:
----------------
Joke MOD - UFO2 The Space Station (v1.0)
----------------

This is a joke MOD of \"The 1970 British science fiction television series UFO\".

The space station can be used as a residence .
This doesn\'t appear on \"television series UFO\".


---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver 1.5.24.0 -


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and overwrite Skyrim Data folder.


---
Ver 1.0 :

Double bed x4
No respawn container x20
Disply case x4
Automatic bookshelf x8
Cooking Pot
Shrine of Talos
Alchemy Workbench
Enchanting Workbench
Smelter Marker
BlackSmith Forge
Armor Workbench 
Blacksmith Sharpening Wheel
Tanning Rack Marker


---
Enjoy!

by hdela
